# Promptology Extension - Claude Code Agent Instructions

> **Specialized instructions for Claude Code assisting with Promptology Chrome extension development**

## Project Context

**Promptology** is a Chrome Manifest V3 browser extension that enables users to execute AI prompts across multiple LLM platforms (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, POE, Grok) directly from a right-click context menu with smart prompt management, favorites, and variable substitution.

**Project Location**: `/Users/sean/Documents/GitHub/Promptology - Ext/`

